    "code": "import flopscope as fnp\n\nx = fnp.array([[0, 2], [1, 1], [2, 0]]).T\n\nx\n\nfnp.cov(x)\n\nx = [-2.1, -1,  4.3]\n\ny = [3,  1.1,  0.12]\n\nX = fnp.stack((x, y), axis=0)\n\nfnp.cov(X)\n\nfnp.cov(x, y)\n\nfnp.cov(x)",
